        <news>v.1.0.2[CR]-Optimized Code.[CR]-Increased Guide Data (default: 1-day, max: 3-days).[CR]-Auto Hide Recordings and Schedules when not in use.[CR]-Improved recording.</news>
        <forum>https://forum.kodi.tv/showthread.php?tid=335116</forum>
